The Online Hotel Booking Application is a full-fledged Web Application. The 
Users can search for hotels, ins, houses, holiday apartments, and other accomodations 
they want. Details of the hotels or other accomodations can be viewed.
Online Hotel Booking Application, as described above, can lead to error free, 
secure, reliable and fast management of the hotel booking. It can assist the admin to 
concentrate on theirother activities rather than to concentrate on record keeping. Thus 
it will help the hotels in better utilization of resources. Admin can maintain
computerized records without redundant entries.
